                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Morgan</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Seoul</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-11-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 28, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Morgan reports that the legation property and archives have been delivered
                    to the American consul-general at Seoul, and that he has informed the Korean
                    minister for foreign affairs of his withdrawal from Korea.)</p>
            </div>
